Key Match Events: Miguel Terceros scored a winning goal in the 58th minute.
Hector Cuellar received a 20th-minute red card.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Bolivia's matches are now being played in El Alto, which is 400m higher than their usual venue.
Bolivia last qualified for the World Cup in 1994.
The top six finishers in the South American qualifiers will automatically qualify for the 2026 World Cup in North America.
